{"tid":2358514,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚千奇唔好staycation!!!","createTime":"2021-01-08T07:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T13:39:57.000Z","uid":126053,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2164367311c735960c6f0aea1bfa31a5b7cddd8f","tid":2358514,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:50:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我係一個毒撚。<br />\n<br />\n尋日終於約到班兄弟去酒店staycation，傾訴一下呢年點樣比女神玩弄於股掌之間嘅經歷。<br />\n<br />\n開心完一晚 朝早去check out<br />\n喺排隊checkout 果陣見到一個高大型男 拖住一個好似我女神嘅女仔退房。<br />\n<br />\n我一路凝望住個男仔，佢成功同我女神staycation， 個額頭刻住咗勝利兩個字。<br />\n<br />\n女神一路同個男仔有講有笑，直到佢見到我失望咁樣望住佢。<br />\n<br />\n女神立刻向後倒退咗3 步再飲咗幾啖水。<br />\n唔知係咪擔心比我聞到佢閪水 同埋個口果浸精味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，我拎出電話打比女神，電話響起，女神殘忍咁樣cut 線， 明明我都只係想同女神講聲我睇你唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我之後WhatsApp 女神， 問佢一唔一齊食lunch， 佢到依家都冇覆我。<br />\n究竟點先可以開解女神？<br />\n我唔介意佢不守婦道<br />\n只係介意佢唔同我做愛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae0a9c77ef89410f6f0dafc9bb19a94ecbc250a","tid":2358514,"uid":173033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:53:22.000Z","msg":"JM9?"},{"pid":"0199bac5a5a43bc5d95b914038587a43f2796a8f","tid":2358514,"uid":382494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4186c13a20214955275198a290899886a4f7e691","tid":2358514,"uid":38317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0199bac5a5a43bc5d95b914038587a43f2796a8f","tid":2358514,"uid":382494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:03:49.000Z","msg":"你肯定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2208665254ff3946816df2cff1f1959a580bf7b","tid":2358514,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0199bac5a5a43bc5d95b914038587a43f2796a8f","tid":2358514,"uid":382494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"新即刻駁嘴/石頭出糧"},{"pid":"9e243fcf8425ef9e2bffbae7ab538786ce39db98","tid":2358514,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"推到變潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都係有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e7c0c954608ef69ed98215e6684962c0dc9378","tid":2358514,"uid":128120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"毒撚點會有成班兄弟一齊去<br />\n垃圾post <br />\n拉"},{"pid":"307edfa54361d524ca9d2e3fc8a5bd4ce500cea0","tid":2358514,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22e7c0c954608ef69ed98215e6684962c0dc9378","tid":2358514,"uid":128120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:22:15.000Z","msg":"毒撚點會有成班兄弟一齊去<br />\n垃圾post <br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"h